20Shark%20Tank%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Shark%20Tank%2C%20we%20underwent%20a%20deep%20rebranding%20process.%20The%20word%20%26quot%3Bmother%26quot%3B%20was%20replaced%20with%20bright%2C%20bold%20images%20because%20we%20couldn't%20trademark%20the%20name.%20We%20changed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdrinkpoppi.com%2Fpages%2Four-story%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ename%20to%20Poppi%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20relaunched%20it%20in%20March%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20role%20is%20chief%20brand%20officer%2C%20which%20means%20I%20run%20our%20creative%20team%20and%20shape%20the%20brand%20and%20vision.%20Stephen%20is%20the%20chief%20product%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20constantly%20communicate%20with%20my%20team%20through%20text%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-teams%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%20Teams%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20email%2C%20and%20phone%20calls%20%E2%80%94%20I%20get%20over%20100%20texts%20and%20400%20emails%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20a%20typical%20day%20looks%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22615d5679-94e4-4a89-b6a2-ac65bb266034%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EEvery%20morning%2C%20my%20three%20children%20wake%20up%20around%205%3A45%20a.m.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20children%20are%202%2C%206%2C%20and%208.%20When%20we%20get%20up%2C%20it's%20full-on%20chaos.%20Stephen%20is%20incredible.%20If%20I'm%20traveling%2C%20he'll%20take%20care%20of%20the%20kids%20and%20let%20me%20sleep%20until%206%3A30%20a.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20have%20a%20morning%20routine.%20I%20make%20lunches%2C%20fill%20water%20bottles%2C%20and%20get%20the%20older%20two%20kids%20ready%20for%20school.%20We%20put%20them%20on%20their%20bikes%2C%20and%20they%20ride%20themselves%20to%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20get%20myself%20and%20the%20baby%20ready%2C%20and%20then%20I%20usually%20drop%20him%20off%20at%20day%20care%20around%208%20a.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22be5af8da-91a7-4c87-9e57-46065f284f16%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'm%20then%20off%20to%20a%20plane%20if%20I'm%20traveling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETravel%20days%20are%20different%20from%20typical%20days.%20Sometimes%2C%20I%20fly%20to%20Boston%20to%20speak%20at%20Harvard%20and%20then%20to%20Montreal%20to%20meet%20agencies%20and%20shoot%20content.%20Then%2C%20I%20hop%20from%20Montreal%20to%20New%20York%20to%20shoot%20a%20live%20podcast.%20I%20try%20to%20be%20super%20available%20and%20work%20through%20my%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20speaking%2C%20which%20involves%20a%20lot%20of%20content%20creation.%20Between%20organic%20and%20paid%20traffic%2C%20we%20have%20about%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40drinkpoppi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20two%20billion%20views%20on%20TikTok%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20create%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fdrinkpoppi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2050%20to%20100%2B%20pieces%20of%20content%3C%2Fa%3E%20every%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20go%20to%20another%20city%2C%20we'll%20add%20an%20extra%20day%20for%20me%20to%20shoot%20content.%20I'll%20visit%20grocery%20stores%2C%20walk%20up%20and%20down%20the%20streets%2C%20interview%20people%2C%20and%20shoot%20trends%20and%20commercials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20the%20Lakers'%20official%20soda%2C%20so%20I%20became%20their%20honorary%20captain.%20I%20then%20shot%20content%20and%20represented%20our%20big%20launch%20in%20October%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223359%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20couple%20sits%20courtside%20at%20a%20Lakers%20game%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e581ae63d72727e1986d94%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222519%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEllsworth%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20Stephen%2C%20at%20a%20Lakers%20game.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Poppi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229299f349-aa86-4c5f-90aa-349adb88ab36%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIf%20I'm%20not%20traveling%2C%20I%20have%20a%2015-minute%20drive%20to%20the%20office%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20visit%20the%20Austin%20office%20five%20days%20a%20week%20if%20I'm%20home.%20We%20started%20as%20a%20remote%20company%20during%20the%20pandemic%20but%20now%20have%20in-person%20teams%20in%20the%20East%2C%20Central%2C%20and%20West.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPoppi%20grew%20from%20two%20employees%20to%20over%20200%20in%20four%20years.%20There%20are%2020%20of%20us%20here%20in%20Austin.%20I%20usually%20have%20one-on-one%20meetings%20with%20our%20team%20and%20shoot%20content%20in%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2239298529-426d-43f0-a848-3baa505ab284%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20don't%20think%20I've%20ever%20taken%20a%20formal%20lunch%20break%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20eat%20my%20lunch%20at%20my%20desk%20and%20while%20on%20Zoom%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20fear%20doing%20a%20lunch%20meeting%20with%20my%20mouth%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20strive%20for%20and%20love%20chaos%20and%20busy%20schedules.%20I'm%20a%20creative%20person%2C%20so%20I'm%20very%20unorganized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20new%20initiative%20arises%2C%20I'm%20usually%20one%20of%20the%20first%20to%20help%20set%20the%20strategy.%20I%20get%20meetings%20put%20on%20my%20calendar%20from%20every%20department%20back%20to%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20shared%20calendar%20and%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexecutive-assistant-salary-job-description-skills-interview-tips-recruiter-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexecutive%20assistant%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20helps%20manage%20my%20schedule.%20I've%20tried%20to%20improve%20my%20organization%2C%20but%20if%20someone%20sees%20an%20hour%20open%20on%20my%20schedule%2C%20they'll%20fill%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bfcdb21e-09ef-45e3-b0db-3820a4b787c5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20leave%20the%20office%20around%206%20p.m.%2C%20commute%20home%2C%20and%20have%20a%20family%20dinner%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECooking%20is%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20things%20to%20do.%20I%20try%20to%20shut%20my%20computer%20when%20I%20get%20home.%20I'm%20with%20my%20family%20for%20at%20least%20one%20hour%20at%20night%2C%20even%20if%20the%20kids%20are%20screaming%2C%20running%20around%2C%20and%20jumping%20on%20the%20tables.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20services%20like%20Marley%20Spoon%2C%20where%20all%20the%20ingredients%20are%20there%20and%20you%20can%20make%20dinner%20in%2020%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20it's%20a%20busy%20week%2C%20we'll%20stop%20on%20the%20way%20home%20to%20get%20tacos.%20Our%20schedule%20is%20not%20so%20structured%20that%20every%20meal%20has%20to%20be%20perfectly%20cooked%20every%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ff79ec05-7a2d-431d-a00d-7c661fc54ffa%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20include%20self-care%20in%20my%20schedule%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20spending%20time%20with%20my%20kids.%20Working%20out%2C%20meditating%2C%20reading%2C%20or%20other%20traditional%20things%20people%20say%20are%20not%20part%20of%20my%20self-care%20routine.%20I%20love%20rewarding%20myself%20with%20shopping%20and%20getting%20my%20nails%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20family%20loves%20Poppi.%20My%20kids%20have%20at%20least%20two%20cans%20a%20day%2C%20and%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20probably%20drink%20three%20cans%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20a%20Poppi%20fridge%20in%20our%20garage%2C%20and%20sometimes%2C%20kids%20in%20the%20neighborhood%20ring%20our%20doorbell%20and%20ask%20for%20a%20Poppi.%20We%20go%20through%2050%20to%20100%20cans%20a%20week%20at%20our%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229cfd657b-63f1-4efd-a1c6-52c6efb03f61%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAfter%20dinner%2C%20it's%20quickly%20off%20to%20baths%20and%20bedtime%20for%20the%20kids%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223187%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20couple%20sits%20in%20bed%20with%20a%20bunch%20of%20pizza%20while%20wearing%20robes%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e581ee69253ccddf9a7b60%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222390%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEllsworth%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20Stephen.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Poppi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20dinner%2C%20we%20leave%20the%20kitchen%20messy%20and%20focus%20on%20the%20kids.%20We%20read%20books%2C%20do%20a%20puzzle%2C%20and%20try%20not%20to%20turn%20on%20the%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20go%20to%20bed%20around%208%20p.m.%2C%20we%20clean%20up%20around%20the%20house.%20I%20then%20get%20in%20bed%20with%20a%20glass%20of%20wine%2C%20put%20on%20a%20show%2C%20and%20the%20computer%20reopens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20read%20emails%2C%20review%20PowerPoint%20decks%2C%20approve%20them%2C%20and%20get%20back%20to%20people%20waiting%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20work%20for%20an%20hour%20or%20two%20while%20watching%20TV%20and%20then%20get%20to%20bed%20around%2011%20p.m.%20Since%20I'm%20a%20night%20owl%2C%20if%20I'm%20in%20the%20groove%2C%20I'll%20work%20until%20midnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20average%2C%20I%20get%20six%20to%20seven%20hours%20of%20sleep%20at%20most.%20Then%20I%20wake%20up%20and%20do%20it%20all%20over%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fday-in-the-life-poppi-cofounder-cbo-allison-ellsworth-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743152701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e5821769253ccddf9a7b78%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fday-in-the-life-poppi-cofounder-cbo-allison-ellsworth-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Allison%20Ellsworth%20relaunched%20her%20prebiotic%20soda%20brand%20as%20Poppi%20in%20March%202020.%20PepsiCo%20announced%20it%20will%20acquire%20Poppi%20for%20%241.95%20billion%20this%20month.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ehochberg%40insider.com%20(Kimanzi%20Constable)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22