20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMUHLX%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20certainly%20thinks%20an%20inflationary%20period%20is%20in%20store%20for%20the%20US%20as%20Trump%20tries%20to%20inflate%20away%20the%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20reasons%20to%20believe%20we%20will%2C%26quot%3B%20Muhlenkamp%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThe%20government's%20borrowed%20too%20much%2C%20and%20the%20solution%20governments%20like%20to%20use%20is%20to%20devalue%20the%20currency%20to%20solve%20the%20debt%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b8e233fc-3bcb-4936-8c5c-ea1a02217f31%5C%22%3ERising%20national%20debt%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rising%20national%20debt%20is%20one%20of%20the%20economy's%20biggest%20concerns%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-investor-fund-manager-beat-sp500-aegis-scott-barbee-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EScott%20Barbee%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20manager%20of%20the%20Aegis%20Value%20Fund%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Ffunds%2Faegis-value-fund-class-i-us00761l1026%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAVALX%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20US%20now%20having%20%2436%20trillion%20of%20debt%2C%20it's%20an%20unsustainable%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20Barbee%20said.%20%26quot%3BA%201%25%20increase%20in%20the%20debt%20will%20lead%20to%20%24360%20billion%20more%20of%20deferral%20spending%20just%20to%20support%20interest%20payments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FDV2aa%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22US%20federal%20debt%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22412%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20national%20debt%20has%20steadily%20crept%20up%20over%20the%20past%20two%20decades.%20At%20the%20start%20of%202008%2C%20the%20debt-to-GDP%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffred.stlouisfed.org%2Fseries%2FGFDEGDQ188S%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20ratio%3C%2Fa%3E%20stood%20at%2064%25.%20Fast%20forward%20to%20today%2C%20and%20the%20ratio%20sits%20at%20over%20120%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeft%20unchecked%2C%20high%20debt%20levels%20could%20harm%20US%20credibility%20in%20global%20markets.%20US%20Treasurys%20are%20seen%20as%20a%20risk-free%20asset%2C%20but%20their%20status%20as%20the%20world's%20most%20trustworthy%20currency%20could%20be%20damaged%20if%20investors%20no%20longer%20deem%20the%20US%20a%20creditworthy%20borrower%20and%20US%20credit%20ratings%20are%20downgraded%2C%20Ocean%20Park%20Asset%20Management's%20CIO%20James%20St.%20Aubin%20wrote%20in%20a%20recent%20note.%20In%20a%20worst-case%20scenario%2C%20the%20market%20could%20see%20a%20massive%20Treasury%20bond%20sell-off%20as%20investors%20dump%20their%20holdings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESt.%20Aubin%2C%20Barbee%2C%20and%20Muhlenkamp%20aren't%20too%20optimistic%20about%20the%20government's%20ability%20to%20reign%20in%20the%20debt.%20While%20details%20aren't%20finalized%2C%20Trump%20has%20made%20tax%20cuts%20a%20big%20part%20of%20his%20campaign%20platform%2C%20which%20would%20only%20drive%20debt%20levels%20even%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226fd1147b-2e1f-416b-a41f-0020bdd4cf97%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20you%20really%20inflate%20away%20the%20debt%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIs%20inflation%20really%20a%20cheat%20code%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20debt%3F%20Maybe%20you're%20wondering%20if%20it'll%20work%20on%20your%20student%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETechnically%2C%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20countries%20get%20into%20this%20kind%20of%20situation%20and%20the%20fiscal%20debt%20is%20denominated%20in%20a%20currency%20the%20country%20controls%20like%20the%20dollar%2C%20the%20way%20that%20this%20gets%20handled%20is%20through%20the%20debasement%20of%20the%20currency%2C%26quot%3B%20Barbee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20government%20adopts%20expansionary%20monetary%20policies%20such%20as%20printing%20money%2C%20lowering%20interest%20rates%2C%20or%20quantitative%20easing%2C%20inflation%20increases.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20real%20value%20of%20the%20debt%20decreases%20as%20the%20US%20dollar's%20purchasing%20power%20erodes%2C%20and%20the%20US%20government%20can%20repay%20its%20debt%20with%20currency%20that's%20worth%20less%20than%20when%20the%20debt%20was%20issued.%20The%20debt-to-GDP%20ratio%20also%20shrinks%20because%20inflation%20increases%20nominal%20GDP%20while%20chipping%20away%20at%20the%20real%20value%20of%20outstanding%20debt%2C%20making%20debt%20a%20smaller%20portion%20of%20the%20overall%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20been%20calling%20for%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finterest-rates-fed-inflation-trump-tariffs-rate-cuts-trade-war-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elower%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20would%20stimulate%20the%20economy.%20Lower%20rates%20also%20makes%20it%20cheaper%20to%20borrow%20money%2C%20which%20would%20lead%20to%20less%20money%20owed%20in%20interest%20on%20the%20national%20debt%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInflation%20isn't%20an%20airtight%20solution%20to%20the%20deficit%20problem%2C%20though.%20If%20inflation%20runs%20unchecked%2C%20it%20could%20end%20up%20triggering%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstagflation-recession-us-economic-outlook-inflation-growth-unemployment-torsten-slok-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estagflation%3C%2Fa%3E%20scenario%20that%20handicaps%20economic%20growth%20and%20sends%20the%20US%20sliding%20into%20a%20recession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Barbee%20doesn't%20see%20immediate%20cause%20for%20concern%2C%20he%20suspects%20the%20US%20government%20might%20not%20be%20able%20to%20kick%20the%20can%20down%20the%20road%20for%20much%20longer%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20see%20a%20way%20out%20of%20it%20in%20the%20longer%20