ster%20than%20is%20typical%20of%20the%20government%2C%20at%20least.%20Point72%20Ventures%20defense%20tech%20partner%20Chris%20Morales%2C%20who's%20based%20in%20DC%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Epointed%20to%20Defense%20Secretary%20Pete%20Hegseth's%20March%20memo%20about%20the%20DoD's%20plans%20to%20modernize%20how%20it%20acquires%20software%20and%20contracts%20with%20companies.%20Morales%20said%20the%20memo%20is%20one%20of%20multiple%20signs%20his%20firm%20is%20seeing%20that%20the%20agency%20is%20getting%20more%20serious%20about%20tech%20innovation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Soya%20and%20Barlia%20said%20they're%20seeing%20startups%20across%20various%20industries%20gain%20traction%20in%20DC%2C%20defense%20tech%20easily%20remains%20the%20hottest%20among%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECape%20landed%20its%20first%20contract%20with%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%20in%202023%2C%20a%20deal%20to%20provide%20its%20cybersecurity-focused%20mobile%20carrier%20services%20to%20Naval%20forces%20in%20Guam%20after%20a%20Chinese%20state-sponsored%20hacking%20group%20targeted%20the%20base's%20tech%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECape%20has%20since%20raised%20%2461%20million%20in%20financing%20rounds%20led%20by%20Andreessen%20Horowitz%20and%20A*%2C%20announced%20in%20April%202024.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22926%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22John%20Doyle%2C%20Cape%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e463bc69253ccddf9a64c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22695%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJohn%20Doyle%2C%20CEO%20and%20founder%20of%20Cape.%3Cp%3ECape%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPart%20of%20the%20reason%20Cape%20picked%20DC%20as%20its%20headquarters%20was%20to%20rub%20shoulders%20with%20the%20federal%20agencies%20it%20hoped%20to%20partner%20with%2C%20said%20Doyle.%20As%20he%20noted%2C%20%26quot%3Bproximity%20matters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20no%20surprise%20then%20that%20a%20number%20of%20defense%20tech%20startups%20have%20opened%20offices%20in%20DC%2C%20including%20Anduril%2C%20which%20recently%20raised%20%241.5%20billion%20at%20a%20%2414%20billion%20valuation%20in%20August%202024%2C%20and%20Shield%20AI%2C%20which%20raised%20%24240%20million%20this%20month%20in%20a%20funding%20round%20that%20valued%20the%20autonomous%20drone%20maker%20at%20%245.3%20billion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStartups%20in%20the%20DMV%20can%20also%20tap%20into%20the%20area's%20hard%20tech%20talent%2C%20which%20could%20help%20continue%20to%20boost%20the%20area's%20presence%20as%20a%20tech%20hub.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENorthern%20Virginia%20hosts%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20concentrations%20of%20data%20centers.%20Amazon%20opened%20its%20second%20headquarters%20in%20Arlington%2C%20Virginia%2C%20in%202023.%20Other%20tech%20giants%2C%20including%20Microsoft%20and%20Google%2C%20have%20outposts%20in%20the%20area.%20And%20many%20of%20the%20country's%20largest%20aerospace%20and%20defense%20companies%2C%20including%20Lockheed%20Martin%20and%20Boeing%2C%20are%20headquartered%20in%20the%20DMV.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDoyle%20said%20the%20DMV's%20deep%20bench%20of%20technical%20expertise%20has%20helped%20Cape%20find%20numerous%20backend%20engineers%20in%20the%20area.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHe%20admitted%2C%20though%2C%20that%20DC%20has%20a%20smaller%20candidate%20pool%20than%20traditional%20tech%20hubs%20like%20San%20Francisco%20and%20New%20York%20City.%20Cape%20also%20has%20a%20New%20York%20office%2C%20for%20which%20Doyle%20said%20it's%20generally%20easier%20to%20source%20talent%2C%20especially%20front-end%20engineers%20and%20designers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b3818a73-a702-4093-af9c-effaec32d0e1%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpposing%20pressures%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20some%20VCs%20flock%20to%20the%20DC%20area%2C%20others%20are%20fleeing.%20Sequoia%20Capital%20plans%20to%20shutter%20its%20DC%20office%20at%20the%20end%20of%20March%20and%20cut%20its%20policy%20team%20there%2C%20despite%20other%20major%20VC%20firms%20moving%20in.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20Sequoia%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20firm%20built%20its%20policy%20team%20in%20DC%20to%20strengthen%20its%20connections%2C%20and%20its%20portfolio%20companies'%20connections%2C%20with%20policymakers%20and%20other%20experts.%20The%20policy%20team%20set%20Sequoia%20up%20favorably%20to%20carry%20those%20relationships%20forward%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Europe%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKhosla%20Ventures%20managing%20director%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frabois-ai-openai-helping-bay-area-tech-venture-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Keith%20Rabois%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20said%20at%20a%20conference%20in%20February%20that%20DC%20%26quot%3Bdefinitely%20still%20is%20not%20where%20early-stage%20venture%20capitalists%20should%20be%20spending%20too%20much%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20despite%20saying%20he'd%20recently%20run%20into%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20and%20Nvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224407%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Keith%20Rabois%20speaks%20on%20a%20stage%20wearing%20a%20yellow%20seater%20and%20dark%20pants%20while%20raising%20his%20hand%20and%20speaking%20to%20an%20interviewer%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e465e963d72727e198579d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223305%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKhosla%20Ventures'%20Rabois%20said%20in%20February%20that%20DC's%20tech%20scene%20still%20can't%20compete%20with%20the%20Bay%20Area's.%3Cp%3ERafael%20Suanes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDC's%20venture%20scene%20may%20not%20yet%20rival%20San%20Francisco's%2C%20but%20it's%20feeling%20fresh%20momentum%20nonetheless.%20A16z's%20American%20Dynamism%20Summit%20largely%20set%20out%20to%20connect%20San%20Francisco's%20VC%20ecosystem%20with%20DC%20policymakers%2C%20but%20DC-based%20investors%20were%20also%20in%20attendance%20this%20year%2C%20said%20Jonathan%20Lacoste%2C%20a%20general%20partner%20at%20Austin%2C%20Texas-based%20Space%20VC%2C%20who%20attended%20the%20conference.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20plenty%20of%20investors%20at%20the%20event%2C%20not%20just%20from%20the%20West%20Coast%2C%20but%20increasingly%20from%20DC's%20venture%20landscape%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20DC's%20tech%20community%20grows%2C%20so%20does%20its%20appetite%20for%20more%20networking%20opportunities.%20Catherine%20McMillan%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20tech-focused%20consulting%20firm%20Booz%20Allen%20Hamilton%2C%20founded%20the%20DC%20chapter%20of%20the%20GenAI%20Collective%2C%20a%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-evolution-software-companies-develop-ai-agents-workforce-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20generative%20AI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20networking%20nonprofit%20started%20in%20San%20Francisco%20in%202023.%20McMillan%20also%20helps%20run%20two%20other%20tech%20communities%20in%20the%20district%3A%20DC%20Tech%20Parties%20and%20She's%20In%20Tech.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMcMillan's%20DC%20chapter%20of%20the%20GenAI%20collective%20now%20has%20700%20members%2C%20with%20each%20event%20bringing%20in%20fresh%20faces.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20undervalued%20tech%20market%20because%20it%20doesn't%20have%20the%20same%20level%20of%20visibility%20that%20SF%20or%20New%20York%20have.%20That's%20part%20of%20what%20I'm%20trying%20to%20do%2C%20shed%20a%20light%20on%20the%20cool%20entrepreneurial%20things%20t