%20of%20the%20Dhoni-factor.%20Ever%20since%20Dhoni%20announced%20his%20retirement%20from%20international%20cricket%2C%20fans%20only%20get%20the%20chance%20to%20watch%20him%20play%20during%20the%20IPL%20as%20he%20does%20not%20play%20any%20other%20form%20of%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20former%20CSK%20batter%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ambati%20Rayudu%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1003-ambati-rayudu-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAmbati%20Rayudu%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggested%20that%20the%20fans%20in%20Chennai%20are%20Dhoni%20supporters%20first%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20%26quot%3Bstrange%26quot%3B%20obsession%20does%20not%20serve%20the%20franchise%20%26quot%3Bwell.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20quite%20strange%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20it%20actually%20serves%20the%20game%20well.%20It%20is%20quite%20daunting%20if%20you're%20a%20newcomer.%20It's%20quite%20loud.%20The%20support%20is%20phenomenal.%20But%2C%20as%20you%20go%20on%20and%20play%2C%20then%20you%20realise%20they%20are%20MS%20Dhoni%20fans%20before%20they%20are%20CSK%20fans.%20It%20is%20quite%20evident%2C%20and%20rightly%20so%2C%20because%20that's%20the%20way%20the%20team%20has%20been%20set%20up%20and%20built%20over%20the%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Rayudu%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DY-Isz-kC1Pc%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EESPNCricinfo%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20rightly%20named%20Thala%20and%20he%20has%20been%20calling%20the%20shots%20in%20CSK%2C%20and%20it's%20come%20to%20a%20stage%20where%20people%20are%20madly%20in%20awe%20and%20in%20love%20of%20what%20he's%20done%20for%20CSK%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERayudu%20also%20pointed%20out%20how%20the%20CSK%20fans%20often%20cheer%20when%20their%20players%20get%20out%20so%20that%20they%20can%20watch%20Dhoni%20bat.%20For%20the%20unversed%2C%20CSK%20fans%20were%20cheering%20the%20dism