agency%20has%20veered%20off%20track%20%E2%80%94%20doubling%20in%20size%20and%20turning%20into%20a%20sprawling%20leviathan%20plagued%20by%20mission%20creep%2C%20financial%20mismanagement%2C%20and%20waste%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20SBA%20Administrator%20Kelly%20Loeffler%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sba.gov%2Farticle%2F2025%2F03%2F21%2Fsmall-business-administration-announces-agency-wide-reorganization%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20press%20release%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Several%20grants%20are%20being%20terminated%20including%20the%20Community%20Navigator%20Pilot%20Program%20that%20awarded%20funding%20to%20small%20businesses%20in%20underserved%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20like%20the%20small%20business%20owners%20we%20support%2C%20we%20must%20do%20more%20with%20less%2C%26quot%3B%20Loeffler%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwomen-entrepreneurs-outpacing-men-small-business-barriers-persist-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743148921000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e5afffb8b41a9673fbeb62%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwomen-entrepreneurs-outpacing-men-small-business-barriers-persist-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Digital%20platforms%20have%20helped%20women%20start%20businesses.%20But%20growth%20for%20Black%20women%20is%20anticipated%20to%20slow%20down%20with%20cuts%20to%20DEI%20programs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jdeng%40insider.com%20(Jireh%20Deng)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwomen-entrepreneurs-outpacing-men-small-business-barriers-persist-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Brokerages%20analyse%20US%20tariffs%20impact%20on%20economies%2C%20sectors%20and%20markets%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743148917000%2