%20police%20had%20been%20issuing%20repeated%20summons%2C%20making%20intrusive%20inquiries%2C%20and%20threatening%20him%20with%20coercive%20action%20based%20on%20his%20wife%20Divya's%20false%20complaint%2C%20LiveLaw%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Sankar%20took%20to%20social%20media%20alleging%20that%20an%20ACP%20and%20a%20SI%20demanded%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20from%20him%20to%20release%20his%20friend%20in%20their%20alleged%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%209%2C%20Divya%20preferred%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20Thirumangalam%20police%20that%20following%20Sankar's%20advice%2C%20his%20manager%20Gokul%20Krishnan%20took%20away%20her%20son%20on%20March%203.%20But%20her%20son%20was%20not%20sent%20back%20to%20her%20after%20two%20days%2C%20as%20agreed%20upon%20earlier%2C%20she%20had%20stated%20in%20the%20complaint%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20CSR%20was%20registered%20and%20even%20as%20the%20initial%20inquiry%20was%20on%2C%20Sankar%20made%20an%20allegation%20on%20his%20social%20media%20site%20that%20the%20ACP%20and%20SI%20demanded%20money%20to%20sort%20out%20the%20wrangle%20between%20him%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20the%20release%20said.%20The%20police%20later%20said%20the%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%2C%20Anna%20Nagar%2C%20will%20probe%20the%20allegation%20of%20corruption%20levelled%20against%20the%20Assistant%20Commissioner%20and%20a%20Sub%20Inspector%2C%20by%20Sankar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20had%20on%20Monday%20transferred%20the%20case%20seeking%20the%20custody%20of%20her%20son%2C%20to%20the%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%2C%20Crime%20Against%20Women%20and%20Children%20(CAWC)%20wing%2C%20Chennai%20for%20a%20thorough%20probe.%20In%20her%20complaint%2C%20Divya%20claimed%20that%20she%20and%20her%20nine-year-old%20son%20were%20US%20citizens%2C%20and%20they%20came%20to%20India%20three%20weeks%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESankar%20shared%20a%20video%20with%20his%20son%2C%20claiming%20the%20boy%20was%20happy%20with%20him%20and%