0(I%20am%20simple).%20Narayan%20Murthy%20says%2C%20'main%20ghar%20ke%20bahar%20hu'%20(I%20am%20out%20of%20the%20house).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20remarks%20referenced%20Mr%20Murthy's%20widely-debated%20suggestion%20that%20employees%20should%20work%2070%20hours%20a%20week%2C%20which%20has%20sparked%20sharp%20reactions%2C%20discussions%20and%20memes%20on%20work-life%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDwelling%20on%20Sudha%20Murty%2C%20Kunal%20Kamra%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20two%20years%2C%20she%20was%20the%20mother-in-law%20of%20the%20entire%20UK.%20How%20is%20this%20simplicity%3F%20She%20is%20going%20to%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20simply.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKunal%20Kamra's%20show%20at%20The%20Habitat%20in%20Mumbai's%20Khar%20has%20triggered%20a%20massive%20political%20backlash%20because%20of%20his%20digs%20at%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader%20Eknath%20Shinde.%20On%20Sunday%2C%20Sena%20supporters%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkunal-kamra-row-mumbai-civic-body-bmc-carries-out-demolition-inside-studio-after-political-backlash-over-kunal-kamras-jibe-at-eknath-shinde-7997531%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evandalised%20the%20venue%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkunal-kamra-eknath-shinde-shiv-sena-comedian-habitat-comedy-club-khar-think-even-bjp-doesnt-like-eknath-shinde-kunal-kamra-to-ndtv-amid-row-8007490%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eissued%20threats%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%2036-year-old%20comedian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKunal%20Kamra%20faces%20multiple%20charges%2C%20including%20defamation%20and%20statements%20conducing%20to%20public%20mischief.%20Mumbai%20Police%20has%20also%20registered%20a%20case%20against%20some%20Sena%20supporters%20for%20the%20vandalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20comedian%20has%20now%20approached%20a%20court%20for%20protection%20against%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743145980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F202