0F-47%20(the%20new%206th-gen%20fighter)%20will%20replace%20the%20F-22%20Raptor%20-%20a%20fifth-generation%20air%20superiority%20stealth%20fighter%2C%20which%20has%20been%20in%20service%20for%20over%2020%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'F-47%3A%20Shaping%20the%20future%20of%20warfare'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.af.mil%2FNews%2FArticle-Display%2FArticle%2F4131094%2Fstatement-by-chief-of-staff-of-the-air-force-gen-david-allvin-on-the-usaf-ngad%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20US%20Air%20Force%20Chief%20of%20Staff%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20General%20David%20Allvin%2C%20briefed%20the%20media%20about%20the%20contract%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Next%20Generation%20Air%20Dominance%20Platform%20(the%20F-47)%20contract%20is%20a%20monumental%20leap%20forward%20in%20securing%20America's%20air%20superiority%20for%20decades%20to%20come.%20This%20contract%20reaffirms%20our%20commitment%20to%20maintaining%20the%20United%20States'%20position%20as%20the%20world's%20most%20dominant%20Air%20Force.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EDominate%20the%20Skies%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnGet%20your%20first%20look%20at%20what%20will%20be%20the%20most%20advanced%2C%20lethal%2C%20%26amp%3B%20adaptable%20fighter%20ever%20developed...%20the%20U.S.%20Air%20Force's%20F-47.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fca1CeBABb5%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fca1CeBABb5%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20U.S.%20Air%20Force%20(%40usairforce)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fusairforce%2Fstatus%2F1903135739971252265%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2021%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20F-47%2C%20we%20are%20not%20just%20building%20another%20fighter%20-%20we%20are%20shaping%20the%20future%20of%20warfare%20and%20putting%20our%20enemies%20on%20notice.%20This%20platform%20will%20be%20the%20most%20advanced%2C%20lethal%2C%20and%20adaptable%20fighter%20ever%20developed%20-%20designed%20to%20outpace%2C%20outmanoeuvre%2C%20and%20outmatch%20any%20adversary%20that%20dares%20to%20challenge%20our%20brave%20Airmen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20what%20our%20adversaries%20claim%2C%20the%20F-47%20is%20truly%20the%20world's%20first%20crewed%20sixth-generation%20fighter%2C%20built%20to%20dominate%20the%20most%20capable%20peer%20adversary%20and%20operate%20in%20the%20most%20perilous%20threat%20environments%20imaginable%2C%26quot%3B%20Gen%20Allvin%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20China's%20%26quot%3B6th-generation%20fighter%26quot%3B%20-%20the%20J-36%20-%20which%20took%20social%20media%20by%20a%20storm%20when%20unverified%20pictures%20of%20the%20aircraft%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-flies-brand-new-stealth-fighter-jet-believed-to-be-6th-generation-7336128%5C%22%3Eflying%20over%20Chengdu%20went%3C%2Fa%3E%20viral%20in%20December.%20Information%20on%20the%20Chinese%20programme%20is%20still%20under%20wraps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20called%20F-47%20a%20%26quot%3Bbeautiful%20number%26quot%3B.%20He%20is%20the%2047th%20President%20of%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'From%20Pause%20To%20Full%20Throttle'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NGAD%20programme%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bfamily%20of%20systems%26quot%3B%20to%20establish%20air%20superiority%20and%20operate%20in%20hostile%20territory%20without%20a%20threat%20of%20attack.%20NGAD%20has%20two%20components%3A%20the%20fighter%20programme%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DopGGj1ViJos%26t%3D7s%5C%22%3ECollaborative%20Combat%20Aircraft%20(CCA)%3C%2Fa%3E%20programme%20to%20develop%20variants%20of%20uncrewed%2C%20semiautonomous%20aircraft%20that%20could%20fly%20as%20%26quot%3Bloyal%20wingmen%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20NGAD%20fighter%20or%20other%20fighter%20aircraft.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Financial%20Year%202025%2C%20the%20Biden%20administration%20requested%20%242.75%20billion%20for%20the%20NGAD%20fighter%20programme%20and%20%24557%20million%20for%20the%20CCA.%20According%20to%20a%202020%20US%20Congressional%20Report%2C%20the%20NGAD%20programme%20was%20budgeted%20at%20%249%20billion%20from%20FY2019%20to%20FY2025%2C%20and%20a%20report%20from%20January%202025%20projects%20a%20rise%20in%20budget%20to%20%245.72%20billion%20by%20FY2029.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECost%20overruns%20were%20reported%20as%20the%20main%20reason%20to%20put%20a%20pause%20on%20the%20NGAD%20Fighter%20Program%2C%20with%20officials%20doubting%20the%20Air%20Force's%20ability%20to%20develop%20an%20NGAD%20fighter%20along%20with%20a%20CCA%2C%20B-21%20stealth%20bomber%20-%20a%206th%20generation%20stealth%20aircraft%20-%20and%20the%20development%20and%20procurement%20of%20the%20LGM-35%20Sentinel%20-%20a%20land-based%20intercontinental%20ballistic%20missile%20that%20will%20replace%20the%20Minuteman%20III%20ICBM.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22B-21%20raider%20is%20the%20worlds%20first%20sixth-generation%20aircraft%20to%20reach%20the%20skies%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22B-21%20raider%20is%20the%20worlds%20first%20sixth-generation%20aircraft%20to%20reach%20the%20skies%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fvmpbem2_b21-raider_625x300_27_March_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Csmall%3EB-21%20Raider%20is%20the%20world's%20first%20sixth-generation%20aircraft%20to%20reach%20the%20skies%3C%2Fsmall%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.northropgrumman.com%2F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%202025%20Congressional%20report%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2Fcrs-product%2FIF11681%5C%22%3EAir%20Force%20informed%20Congress%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20%26quot%3BSentinel%20programme%20exceeded%20its%20initial%20cost%20projections%2C%20positing%20at%20least%20a%2037%25%20increase%20(from%20%24118%20million%20initial%20baseline%20cost%20to%20%24162%20million%20in%202020%20dollars)%20in%20the%20cost%20per%20unit.%26quot%3B%20The%20US%20Air%20Force%20plans%20to%20procure%20over%20600%20such%20missiles%20over%20the%20next%20few%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20NGAD%20Fighter%20Program%2C%20the%20Congress%20report%20from%202025%20said%20instead%20of%20building%20a%20new%20aircraft%2C%20the%20Air%20Force%20may%20consider%20a%20different%20approach%20and%20%26quot%3Bdisaggregating%26quot%3B%20major%20subsystems%20such%20as%20the%20radar%20or%20weapons%2C%20and%20moving%20those%20to%20other%20platforms%20such%20as%20CCAs.%20However%2C%20US%20Air%20Force%20Secretary%20Frank%20Kendall%20ordered%20a%20study%20that%20supported%20a%20manned%20aircraft%20and%20left%20it%20to%20the%20Trump%20administration%20to%20decide%20on%20the%20programme's%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%2C%20while%20announcing%20the%20contract%2C%20said%20'He%20can't%20disclose%20the%20cost%20details%20of%20the%20programme%20due%20to%20national%20security%20reasons%2C%20but%20in%202018%2C%20Congress%20was%20informed%20that%20a%20single%20airframe%20of%20NGAD%20would%20cost%20%24300%20million%2C%20which%20is%20significantly%20higher%20than%20any%20US%20aircraft%20currently%20in%20service.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20Senate%20Appropriations%20Committee%20in%20its%20report%20on%20the%20'FY2025%20Defense%20Appropriations'%20committee%20recommended%20%26quot%3Bcutting%20%24557.1%20million%20and%20transferring%20that%20amount%20to%20the%20CCA%20programme.%20The%20Committee%20stated%20that%20the%20NGAD%20and%20the%20CCA%20are%20being%20requested%20on%20the%20same%20funding%20line%2C%20limiting%20visibility%20into%20the%20cost%20and%20performance%20of%20each%20programme%20element.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20F-22%20Raptor%20was%20envisioned%20in%20the%2080s%20to%20replace%20the%20F-15%20as%20a%20more%20potent%20air%20superiority%20fighter.%20The%20aircraft%2C%20built%20by%20Lockheed%20Martin%2C%20entered%20service%20in%202005%2C%20with%20advanced%20technology%2C%20stealth%2C%20supercruise%20and%20manoeuvrability.%20Initially%2C%20750%20F-22s%20were%20planned%20for%20procurement%2C%20but%20four%20years%20into%20the%20service%2C%20the%20US%20Defence%20Secretary%20Robert%20Gates%20paused%20the%20programme%20at%20187%2C%20closing%20its%20assembly%20line.%20An%20F-22%20airframe%20costs%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.af.mil%2FAbout-Us%2FFact-Sheets%2FDisplay%2FArticle%2F104506%2Ff-22-raptor%2F%5C%22%3E%24142%20million%20apiece%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20focus%20then%20moved%20to%20the%20F-35%20Lightning%2C%20a%20multi-role%205th%20gen%20fighter%20used%20by%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%2C%20Navy%20and%20Marines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Foaapnha8_american-f35_625x300_18_February_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Csmall%3EF-35%20Lightning%20-%20a%20multi-role%205th%20gen%20fighter%20used%20by%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%2C%20Navy%20and%20Marines.%3C%2Fsmall%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20F-35's%20advanced%20features%2C%20the%20US%20Government%20Accountability%20Office%20(GAO)%2C%20in%20its%20report%2C%20said%20it%20would%20take%20at%20least%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F1-7-trillion-burden-f-35-fighter-jet-has-high-maintenance-cost-says-report-4999717%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%241.7%20trillion%20to%20purchase%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20operate%20and%20sustain%20the%20aircraft%20in%20its%2066-year%20life%20cycle%20due%20to%20high%20maintenance%20costs%20and%20developmental%20delays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'China%20Is%20A%20Threat%20Today'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20over%20800%20military%20bases%20globally%2C%2011%20aircraft%20carriers%2C%20and%20the%20most%20potent%20defence%20technology%2C%20the%20US%20is%20a%20global%20power%20that%20can%20engage%20and%20operate%20within%20minutes%20in%20any%20part%20of%20the%20world.%20Frank%20Kendall%20refuses%20to%20agree%20with%20China%20being%20a%20%26quot%3Bthreat%20of%20the%20future%26quot%3B%20and%20calls%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bthreat%20today%26quot%3B.%20The%20Congress%20report%2C%20quoting%20analysts%2C%20states%20that%20in%20a%20fight%20with%20China%20(most%20likely%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea)%20where%20islands%20are%20separated%20from%20the%20coast%20by%20hundreds%20of%20kilometres%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BF-22%20may%20be%20constrained%20by%20its%20450%20nautical%20mile%20range%20and%202%2C000-pound%20payload%20capacity.%20For%20greater%20range%2C%20the%20F-22%20relies%20on%20U.S.%20aerial%20refuelling%20tankers%20such%20as%20the%20KC-46%20and%20KC-135%2C%20which%20may%20be%20vulnerable%20to%20attack.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2015-12%2Fus-air-force-lockheed-martin-f-22-raptor-afp_650x400_61450329306.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EF-22%20Raptor%20is%20an%20American%20technological%20marvel.%20It%20is%20the%20world's%20best%20air-superiority%20stealth%20fighter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NGAD%20Fighter%20Program%20was%20envisioned%20to%20counter%20China%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bthreat%20today%26quot%3B%20and%20to%20counter%20anti-access%2Farea-denial%20(A2%2FAD)%20capabilities.%20In%202016%2C%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Science%20Board%20(DSB)%20published%20a%20report%20on%20'Air%20Dominance'%20to%20study%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20effective%20science%2C%20technology%2C%20capability%20and%20systems%20for%20maintaining%20air%20dominance%20beyond%20the%20next%20decade.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20identified%20the%20%26quot%3Brapid%20emergence%20of%20anti-access%20and%20area%20denial%20(A2%2FAD)%20strategies%20advanced%20by%20state%20actors.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%2C%20over%20the%20past%2020%20years%2C%20has%20expanded%20its%20war-fighting%20capabilities%20in%20the%20sea%20with%20a%20web%20of%20anti-ship%2C%20anti-air%2C%20and%20ballistic%20missiles%2C%20aircraft%20carriers%2C%20submarines%2C%20fighter%20jets%2C%20etc.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asianmilitaryreview.com%2F2023%2F03%2Fchinas-stealthy-area-denial%2F%5C%22%3EA2%2FAD%20doesn't%20mean%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3BNo%20access%20to%20enemy%20territory%26quot%3B%2C%20but%20increasing%20the%20radius%20of%20the%20battlezone%2C%20which%20may%20be%20highly%20contested%20or%20under%20threat%2C%20keeping%20the%20adversary%20far%20away%20from%20strategic%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20China's%20growing%20dominance%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%2C%20the%20US%20needed%20a%20new%20fighter%20that%20could%20establish%20air%20superiority%20in%20the%20region%2C%20compensating%20for%20the%20shortfalls%20in%20the%20F-22%20Raptor's%20capabilities%20in%20the%20present%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%202016%20report%20on%20Air%20Superiority%202030%20Flight%20Plan%2C%20the%20need%20%26quot%3Bfor%20a%20family%20of%20integrated%20and%20networked%20'stand-off'%20(weapons%20launched%20from%20a%20distance)%20and%20'stand-in'%20(weapons%20that%20penetrate%20adversary%20territory%20and%20strike%20close%20to%20targets)%20forces.%20It%20sought%20a%20%26quot%3BPenetrating%20Counter%20Air%26quot%3B%20capability%20that%20would%20%26quot%3Bmaximize%20tradeoffs%20between%20range%2C%20payload%2C%20survivability%2C%20lethality%2C%20affordability%2C%20and%20supportability.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20the%20Air%20Force%20acquisition%20executive%2C%20Dr%20Will%20Roper%2C%20said%20the%20Air%20Force%20had%20flown%20a%20full-scale%20flight%20demonstrator%20as%20part%20of%20the%20NGAD%20programme.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%20Chief%20of%20Staff%20Gen%20Allvin%20said%20the%20F-47%20%26quot%3Bwill%20fly%20during%20the%20Trump%20administration%26quot%3B%20because%20%26quot%3BFor%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20the%20X-planes%20for%20this%20aircraft%20have%20been%20quietly%20laying%20the%20foundation%20for%20the%20F-47%20-%20flying%20hundreds%20of%20hours%2C%20testing%20cutting-edge%20concepts%2C%20and%20proving%20that%20we%20can%20push%20the%20envelope%20of%20technology%20with%20confidence.%20These%20experimental%20aircraft%20have%20demonstrated%20the%20innovations%20necessary%20to%20mature%20the%20F-47's%20capabilities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743138600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fchh7bp_f47-us-air-force_625x300_27_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffrom-pause-to-full-throttle-trump-resurrects-us-6th-gen-fighter-program-f-47-f-22-ngad-6th-generation-fighter-8026740%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Eight%20months%20ago%2C%20the%20departing%20Biden%20administration%20halted%20the%20ambitious%20'Next%20Generation%20Air%20Dominance'%20fighter%20programme%2C%20citing%20cost%20overruns.%20Trump%20has%20revived%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffrom-pause-to-full-throttle-trump-resurrects-us-6th-gen-fighter-program-f-47-f-22-ngad-6th-generation-fighter-8026740%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China's%20Tencent%20buys%20stake%20in%20Ubisoft%20unit%20behind%20Assassin's%20Creed%20and%20more%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22publish