0unrest%20and%20nearly%201%2C900%20detentions.%20Demonstrators%2C%20including%20one%20in%20a%20Pikachu%20costume%2C%20were%20seen%20clashing%20with%20the%20police%2C%20as%20international%20concerns%20over%20Turkey's%20democratic%20decline%20grow.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fwatch-pikachu-seen-fleeing-police-during-anti-erdogan-protests-in-turkey%2Farticleshow%2F119630517.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fwatch-pikachu-seen-fleeing-police-during-anti-erdogan-protests-in-turkey%2Famp_articleshow%2F119630517.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fwatch-pikachu-seen-fleeing-police-during-anti-erdogan-protests-in-turkey%2Famp_articleshow%2F119630517.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kolkata%20Curator's%20U-Turn%20After%20Row%20Over%20Denying%20Rahane's%20Pitch%20Request%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESujan%20Mukherjee%2C%20a%20pitch%20curator%20at%20Eden%20Gardens%2C%20has%20been%20receiving%20a%20lot%20of%20backlash%20after%20denying%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(KKR)%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ajinkya%20Rahane%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F965-ajinkya-rahane-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAjinkya%20Rahane%3C%2Fa%3E's%20request%20to%20prepare%20a%20spin-friendly%20track.%20Following%20KKR's%20big%20loss%20to%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20(RCB)%20in%20the%20opening%20match%20of%20IPL%202025%2C%20Rahane%20expressed%20his%20frustration%20over%20the%20pitch%20used%20for%20the%20game%2C%20and%20hoped%20to%20see%20spin-friendly%20track%20at%20the%20Eden%20Gardens.%20%26quot%3BWe%20would%20love%20to%20see%20the%20pitch%20helping%20the%20spin%20bowlers%20but%20again%2C%20this%20wicket%20was%20under%20cover%20for%20the%20last%20one-and-a-half%20days.%20Both%20the%20spinners%20we%20have%2C%20the%20quality%20they%20have%2C%20they%20can%20bowl%20in%20any%20kind%20of%20wicket%20and%20I%20am%20sure%20they%20are%20confident%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Rahane%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20after%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20RevSportz%2C%20Mukherjee%20said%20he%20was%20not%20going%20to%20make%20any%20changes%20and%20even%20gave%20the%20example%20of%20the%20RCB%20spinners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20per%20the%20IPL%20rules%20and%20regulations%2C%20franchises%20have%20no%20say%20over%20the%20pitch.%20Ever%20since%20I%20have%20taken%20charge%20(as%20Eden%20curator)%2C%20the%20pitches%20here%20have%20been%20like%20this.%20It%20was%20like%20this%20in%20the%20past.%20Things%20haven't%20changed%20now%2C%20and%20it%20will%20not%20be%20altered%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Mukherjee%20told%20RevSportz.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTheir%20(RCB)%20spinners%20took%20four%20wickets%20between%20them.%20What%20did%20the%20KKR%20spinners%20do%3F%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Krunal%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64213-krunal-himashu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKrunal%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%20got%20three%20wickets.%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Suyash%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F117309-suyash-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESuyash%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20turned%20the%20ball%20to%20castle%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Andre%20Russell%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1536-andre-russell-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAndre%20Russell%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Mukherjee%2C%20who%20has%20been%20facing%20a%20lot%20of%20flak%20over%20his%20remarks%2C%20has%20backtracked%20from%20his%20previous%20remarks%2C%20saying%20that%20he%20never%20denied%20any%20request%20from%20KKR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20official%20or%20player%20asked%20for%20the%20pitch%20requirement%20for%20the%20first%20match.%20A%20coach%20at%20the%20time%20of%20practice%20asked%20me%20about%20the%20behaviour%20of%20the%20pitch.%20I%20said%20ghumega%20bhi%20aur%20accha%20chalega%20(the%20pitch%20will%20turn%2C%20and%20it%20will%20be%20good%20for%20batting)%2C%26quot%3B%20Mukherjee%20told%20Sports%20Tak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukherjee%20also%20insisted%20he%20has%20good%20relations%20with%20everyone%20at%20KKR%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20pitch%20was%20prepared%20as%20per%20the%20BCCI's%20guidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20never%20denied%20anything%20to%20KKR.%20We%20have%20been%20in%20good%20relations%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20I%20prepared%20the%20pitch%20as%20per%20BCCI%20guidelines.%20Those%20who%20are%20accusing%20me%20know%20nothing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20New%20Zealand%20pacer%20Simon%20Doull%20had%20blasted%20Mukherjee%20for%20denying%20KKR's%20request%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20franchise%20should%20move%20away%20from%20the%20Eden%20Gardens%20if%20they%20don't%20get%20the%20pitch%20as%20per%20their%20liking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20he%20(the%20curator)%20is%20not%20taking%20heed%20of%20what%20the%20home%20team%20wants...%20I%20mean%2C%20they%20are%20paying%20the%20stadium%20fees%2C%20they%20are%20paying%20for%20what's%20going%20on%20in%20the%20IPL%2C%20but%20if%20he's%20still%20not%20paying%20heed%20of%20what%20the%20home%20team%20wants%2C%20then%20just%20move%20the%20franchise%20away%20to%20somewhere%20else.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20job%20is%20not%20to%20pass%20an%20opinion%20on%20the%20game.%20That's%20not%20what%20he's%20paid%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20Doull%20told%20Cricbuzz%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20losing%20to%20RCB%20in%20their%20opening%20match%2C%20KKR%20registered%20their%20first%20win%20of%20the%20season%2C%20on%20the%20road%2C%20against%20the%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20in%20Guwahati.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743134460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F202