%20human%20survival%20on%20the%20Moon%20and%20Mars%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Rachna%20Arora%2C%20a%20Physics%20Educator%20at%20Shiv%20Nadar%20School%2C%20Noida.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20also%20helps%20to%20explore%20how%20crops%20can%20be%20grown%20in%20space%20and%20how%20microgravity%20impacts%20human%20biology.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20were%20astronauts%20Butch%20Wilmore%20and%20Sunita%20Williams%20stuck%20in%20space%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAstronauts%20Butch%20Wilmore%20and%20Sunita%20Williams%20embarked%20on%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360476%2Fnasa-space-camp-for-students-astronauts-geet-alabama-us-space-rocket-centre-how-to-get-apply%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeight-day%20mission%3C%2Fa%3E%20aboard%20the%20Boeing%20Starliner%20(CST-100)%2C%20a%20spacecraft%20designed%20for%20crew%20transport.%20However%2C%20their%20return%20was%20delayed%20due%20to%20a%20helium%20leak%20in%20the%20propulsion%20system%2C%20making%20re-entry%20unsafe.%20%E2%80%9CEntering%20and%20leaving%20Earth%20is%20very%20risky%2C%20and%20this%20spacecraft%20faced%20a%20helium%20leakage%2C%20so%20it%20could%20not%20leave%20the%20ISS%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Rachna.%20Eventually%2C%20they%20returned%20via%20SpaceX%E2%80%99s%20Crew%20Dragon%20capsule%2C%20after%20spending%20nine%20unexpected%20months%20in%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20did%20they%20sustain%20themselves%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20extended%20stay%2C%20Wilmore%20and%20Williams%20had%20enough%20supplies%20to%20survive%20comfortably.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20ISS%20is%20equipped%20to%20sustain%