n%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20journey%20began%20in%202018%20with%20extensive%20research%20and%20development%20in%20freeze-drying%20techniques.%20Alongside%20Amit%20and%20Shalu%2C%20Amit%E2%80%99s%20sister%2C%20Madhu%20Goel%2C%20also%20became%20a%20part%20of%20the%20venture.%20By%202020%2C%20Spice%20Up%20Foods%20was%20producing%20small%20batches%20of%20their%20ready-to-eat%20meals%2C%20initially%20sending%20them%20to%20family%20and%20friends%20for%20feedback.%20The%20key%20was%20maintaining%20the%20taste%20and%20texture%20of%20the%20meals%20after%20freeze-drying.%20%E2%80%9CEach%20batch%20was%20tested%20for%20quality%2C%20with%20rigorous%20checks%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20meals%20were%20preservative-free%20and%20would%20last%20for%20months%20without%20spoiling%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Amit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESteps%20behind%20freeze-drying%20and%20its%20benefits%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20factor%20that%20differentiates%20Spice%20Up%20Foods%20in%20the%20ready-to-eat%20market%20is%20its%20use%20of%20freeze-drying%20technology.%20So%20how%20does%20it%20work%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20process%20begins%20with%20home%20cooks%20preparing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353810%2Ffarm-to-table-experiential-dining-fresh-produce-mharokhet-jodhpur-the-farm-solitude-farm-project-hum-mumbai-goa%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emeals%20using%20fresh%20ingredients%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20just%20like%20they%20would%20in%20their%20kitchens.%20These%20meals%20are%20then%20brought%20to%20our%20facility%20and%20frozen%20at%20a%20very%20low%20temperature%2C%20around%20-40%C2%B0C%2C%20which%20helps%20preserve%20the%20food%E2%80%99s%20texture%20and%20structure.%20After%20freezing%2C%20the%20food%20is%20placed%20in%20a%20vacuum%20chamber%20where%20the%20ice%20within%20the%20food%20sublimates%20(turns%20from%20solid%20directly%20into%20vapour).%20This%20process%20removes%20the%20moisture%20from%20the%20food%2C%20leaving%20behind%20a%20light%20and%20dry%20product%20that%20can%20be%20rehydrated%20by%20simply%20adding%20hot%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shalu%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dehydration%20temperature%20is%20adjusted%20based%20on%20the%20consistency%20of%20the%20food.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20example%2C%20chutneys%20are%20dried%20at%20a%20much%20lower%20temperature%20than%2C%20say%2C%20%3Cem%3Edal%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20%3Cem%3Erajma%3C%2Fem%3E.%20This%20control%20over%20the%20process%20ensures%20that%20each%20dish%20maintains%20the%20same%20texture%2C%20taste%2C%20and%20nutritional%20value%20as%20it%20would%20if%20it%20were%20freshly%20cooked.%20As%20compared%20to%20traditional%20dehydration%20techniques%2C%20which%20can%20extract%20as%20much%20as%2092%20or%2096%20percent%20of%20the%20water%20content%2C%20freeze-drying%20removes%20more%20than%2099%20percent%20of%20the%20water%2C%20so%20we%20decided%20to%20choose%20this%20technique%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.05.12-3_11zon-1742741055-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20duo%20spent%20around%20four%20years%20researching%20the%20right%20temperatures%20for%20the%20freeze-drying%20technique%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.05.12-3_11zon-1742741055-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025