caption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20startup%20helps%20mothers%20send%20homemade%20meals%20to%20their%20children%20studying%20abroad%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20this%20work%2C%20they%20had%20to%20work%20closely%20with%20the%20manufacturers%20of%20freeze-drying%20machines.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20to%20ask%20the%20person%20who%20makes%20these%20machines%20to%20customise%20it%20based%20on%20our%20needs.%20We%20gave%20him%20specific%20measurements%2C%20temperature%20settings%2C%20tray%20sizes%2C%20and%20other%20precise%20details%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Amit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20co-founders%20connected%20with%20several%20suppliers%20for%20key%20components%20of%20the%20machine%2C%20including%20the%20drying%20chamber%2C%20vacuum%20pump%2C%20heat%20source%2C%20condenser%2C%20and%20trays.%20He%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20connected%20with%20around%20four%20or%20five%20different%20people%20for%20all%20the%20parts%20of%20the%20machine.%20Once%20everything%20came%20together%2C%20we%20had%20a%20freeze-drying%20machine%20built%20specifically%20for%20us%2C%20with%20all%20the%20right%20settings%20to%20preserve%20the%20quality%20of%20our%20food.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelping%20homemakers%20become%20financially%20independent%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20key%20aspects%20of%20Spice%20Up%20Foods%E2%80%99%20success%20is%20its%20collaboration%20with%20homemakers.%20The%20couple%2C%20along%20with%20their%20co-founder%20Madhu%2C%20wanted%20to%20empower%20homemakers%2C%20especially%20those%20who%20were%20looking%20to%20make%20use%20of%20their%20culinary%20skills%20while%20also%20earning%20an%20income.%20As%20Amit%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20started%2C%20we%20were%20cooking%20from%20our%20kitchen.%20My%20mother%20and%20Shalu%20would%20mostly%20prepare%20the%20meals.%20But%20soon%2C%20we%20realised%20that%20we%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20scale%20that%20way.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20we%20decided%20to%20bring%20in%20home%20cooks%20and%20help%20them%20turn%20their%20passion%20for%20cooking%20into%20a%20profitable%20business.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhenever%20we%20place%20a%20particular%20order%20with%20a%20home%20cook%2C%20we%20thoroughly%20inspect%20the%20ingredients%20and%20vegetables%20before%20sending%20it%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shalu.%20Once%20the%20food%20is%20prepared%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20transferred%20into%20steel%20containers%2C%20properly%20sealed%2C%20and%20transported%20to%20their%20unit%20for%20further%20processing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHome%20cooks%20with%20their%20own%20transport%20are%20encouraged%20to%20deliver%20meals%20directly%20to%20the%20unit.%20If%20not%2C%20the%20team%20arranges%20pick-ups%20through%20Swiggy%20Genie%20or%20Porter.%20Amit%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20operations%20team%20manages%20everything%20from%20pick-up%20to%20delivery.%20For%20larger%20quantities%2C%20like%20three%20kg%20of%20rajma%2C%20if%20the%20home%20cook%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20suitable%20containers%2C%20we%20provide%20huge%20plastic%20boxes%20for%20them%20to%20fill%20and%20send%20back%20to%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.05.47-1_11zon-1742741435-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Spice%20Up%20foods%20has%20served%20over%2015%2C000%20meals%20across%20India%20and%20internationally%20so%20far%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.05.47-1_11zon-1742741435-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.05.47-1_11zon-1742741435-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.